OL,3,CFormer car dealer alleges practices
OL,4,Callowing mis-selling of motor finance
OL,6,FITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,7,Fhas spoken to a whistle blower who
OL,8,Freveals practices he says harmed
OL,9,Fcustomers' finances
OL,11,FITV News can reveal new evidence about
OL,12,Fthe alleged mis-selling of motor
OL,13,Ffinance deals as millions of UK
OL,14,Fdrivers continue to hope for
OL,15,Fcompensation.
OL,17,FThe Financial Conduct Authority is
OL,18,Finvestigating so-called "discretionary
OL,19,Fcommissions" which allowed dealers to
OL,20,Fvary interest rates on car loans.
