OL,3,CFormer car dealer alleges practices
OL,4,Callowing mis-selling of motor finance
OL,6,FThere's evidence that the higher the
OL,7,Frates, the greater the commissions
OL,8,Fmany of them earned.
OL,10,FNow we've spoken to a whistle blower
OL,11,Fwho reveals practises he says harmed
OL,12,Fcustomers' finances.
OL,14,FHe told us: "They'd come in expecting
OL,15,Fnot to get finance, so they'd just say
OL,16,Fyes to the first offer at 17.9% APR
OL,17,Fwhen realistically we could get them
OL,18,F8.9%, so they were paying top whack
OL,19,Ffor something they didn't have to pay
OL,20,Ftop whack for".
