OL,6,FWe asked him about what information
OL,7,Fbuyers got on commissions earned by
OL,8,Fdealers who sold loans, he told us
OL,9,F"they could request information with
OL,10,Fhead office and we would say it takes
OL,11,F30 days to get that information, but
OL,12,Fwe have to stop the sale, they'd
OL,13,Fbasically then just brush that off and
OL,14,Fsay I want the car before we had to
OL,15,Fdisclose anything".
