OL,4,Callowing mis-selling of motor finance
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Adrian Daly of
OL,7,Fthe Finance and Leasing Association
OL,8,Fsaid there has been no car loans
OL,9,F"scandal" and says few will be
OL,10,Fentitled to payouts.
OL,12,FHe says dealers followed the official
OL,13,Frules on commission disclosures that
OL,14,Fexisted at the time.
OL,16,FHe says most people got good deals
OL,17,Feven when commissions were involved.
OL,19,FBuying a vehicle is second only to
OL,20,Fhouse buying in terms of being one of
OL,21,Fthe biggest purchases most of us make.
